<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="age-vi">age <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /eɪdʒ/    美 /eɪdʒ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>（使）变老；（使）老化：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As your son grows you also age.
你儿子长大的同时你也在变老。</p><footer>2016 天津</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sun's rays can age and harm our skin.
阳光会老化和伤害我们的皮肤。</p><footer>2019 全国</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>aging / ageing /'eɪdʒɪŋ/ n [U]  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an anti-aging treatment
抗衰老的治疗方法</p></div>

<p>aging / ageing  adj   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>China is faced with the challenges of an <strong>ageing population</strong>.
中国正面临着人口老龄化的挑战。</p></div></div>